relation: Clumsy Robot takes up the Guitar

This one came to me as I was watching a bunch of bands playing one night. And yes, I know his head is oval-shaped. Come on, give him money. Guy's food supply can't hold out forever! ...Or can it? ...That Musica doesn't look very happy...
I imagine those gangly robot arms must have a tough time keeping that heavy head upright.
After playing enough of Paper Mario: TTYD, I noticed that Mr. Hoggle, the hot-dog vendor in Glitzville, kind of looked a little like a Pigmask. Yep.
Of the three games overall, this is my favorite zombie character. A zombie armadillo? Certainly didn't see this one coming.
Now he can figure out the length (and width) of things easily!
